fields.name: Gibson LP 57 Black Beauty Gloss
fields.description: The Custom Historic '57 Les Paul Custom Reissue was a tribute to the late-'50s Black Beauty Les Pauls. Features a mahogany body, ebony fretboard, and Burstbucker pickups. Options included two or three pickups, and a Bigsby or stop-bar tailpiece. Available in Ebony VOS or Gloss. Updated in 2015 with Gibson's True Historic Line.

fields.name: Gretsch G6120 Eddie Cochran
fields.description: Gretsch honors the legacy of rock 'n' roll and rockabilly pioneer Eddie Cochran with the G6120 Eddie Cochran Signature Hollow Body model, based on the distinctively modified guitar that fueled Cochran's highly influential and all-too-brief career.

fields.name: Music Man John Petrucci Majesty 6 PN
fields.description: Music Man John Petrucci Majesty 6 CT, Electric Guitar, John Petrucci (Dream Theater) 'Enchanted Forrest' Signature Model, Body: Mahogany
